Preface
WidgetBox Privacy Policy (or “Privacy Policy”, or “Policy” in this article; this Privacy Policy, together with its updated versions, constitutes this “Privacy Policy”), applies to users (or “You”) who have used the products and services provided by the WidgetBox product and service provider (or “WidgetBox Operator” or “We” in this article). This Privacy Policy describes in detail the policies and practices of the WidgetBox Operator with respect to the acquisition, management, and protection of your personal information.
It should be noted that
– The WidgetBox product is a mobile client application with the name of “WidgetBox”.
– The WidgetBox Operator refers to Ningbo Yibin Technology Co., Ltd. (Registered address: Wangjiaqiao Village, Dongqiao Town, Haishu District, Ningbo City, Zhejiang Province, China; Contact address: 28th Floor, Building 1, Yongjiang Talent Innovation Center, No. 2632 Zhongshan Road, Yinzhou District, Ningbo City, Zhejiang Province, China).
Before you use the services provided by the WidgetBox Operator, please be sure to read and understand this Privacy Policy (especially the bolded terms), to understand in detail how we collect and use information, and to choose whether to agree to the relevant content. By selecting “Agree” or “Next” (or other similar operations with different names but of the same nature), you fully understand and agree to sign this agreement, commit to be bound by the agreement as a party to the agreement, and agree to the WidgetBox Operator to handle your personal information in accordance with the agreement of this Privacy Policy. If you disagree with any of the terms of this Agreement or are unable to accurately understand any of the terms of this Agreement, please do not access and/or use the WidgetBox application and its related services.
Minors under the age of eighteen should read this policy with a guardian and use the WidgetBox services only after obtaining their consent to your use of the services and to the terms of this agreement in its entirety.
If you have any comments, suggestions, or questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact us through the methods advertised in this Privacy Policy (you may send the relevant content to xiaozhihe2021@gmail.com) or other contact/feedback channels provided within WidgetBox, and we will answer you as soon as possible.
Part I Definition
Personal information
refers to all kinds of information recorded electronically or otherwise that can identify a specific natural person or reflect the activities of a specific natural person, either alone or in combination with other information.
Sensitive personal information
is personal information that, if leaked, illegally provided or misused, may endanger the safety of persons and property, and is highly likely to lead to damage to a person’s reputation, physical or mental health, or discriminatory treatment, etc.
